'''Syntheway Strings''' is a commercial, proprietary music software synthesizer for the Microsoft Windows platform, developed by [[Syntheway]] Virtual Musical Instruments.

The software can be used to emulate a Violin, Viola, Cello and Double Bass working as a plugin within digital audio workstation software such as [[FL Studio]], Cubase or [[Ableton Live]].


==Characteristics==

Syntheway Strings is a sample based musical instrument developed as a [[VST]] plug-in and designed to recreate the Strings Ensemble.


==MIDI Automation==

Features complete [[MIDI]] Continuous Controller to automate parameter changes from a sequencer, or to control the Syntheway Strings software from an external MIDI control surface.


==Strings Selector==

* Full Strings 
* Octaves Strings 
* Dark Strings 
* Marcato Strings 
* Staccato Strings 
* Marcato Octaves 
* Synth Strings 1 
* Synth Strings 2 
* Hybrid Strings 
* Pizzicato Strings  


